# No Hardware Edits

Do not modify any files under `**/hardware/` directories in this project.

- Do not edit KiCad schematics (`.kicad_sch`), PCBs (`.kicad_pcb`), or project files
- Do not edit BOMs, production artifacts, or fabrication configs under hardware
- If the user asks to change hardware, suggest they make edits in KiCad (or their EDA tool) directly, or explain what to change without applying edits

You may still read hardware files to answer questions or understand the design.
